title: Superior Carnage 03 (of 05) (2013) (Digital) (Nahga-Empire)
description: IT'S ALIVE! The Wizard finally unveils Carnage's BRAND NEW LOOK and releases his personal AGENT OF EVIL out into the world.But can the new FRIGHTFUL FOUR control their newest member? Or will the team be destroyed from within?KEVIN SHINICK (Robot Chicken, Avenging Spider-Man) and STEPHEN SEGOVIA (X-treme X-Men) strike at the heart of their own creation with an electrifying story that shouldn't be missed!
